Package mapeditor

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IContinent
    This class is responsible for managing the continents loaded from file.
    IEditor
    This class initializes the map editor and asks user for options to modify the map.
    IEditorBasicProp
    The class lets the user modify the basic properties of map.
    IEditorContinent
    The class for editing the continent
    IEditorTerritory
    This class provides options for modifications of territories.
    ILoadedMap
    This class contains data structures into which the map is loaded.
    IMapLoader
    This class loads the map into data structures.
    ITerritory
    The class to load territory in data structures.
    IVerification
    This class verifies map data in data structures.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Continent
    This class is responsible for managing the continents loaded from file.
    Editor
    This class initializes the map editor and asks user for options to create and modify the map.
    EditorBasicProp
    The class lets the user modify the basic properties of map.
    EditorContinent
    The class for editing the continent
    EditorTerritory
    This class provides options for modifications of territories.
    LoadedMap
    This class contains data structures into which the map is loaded.
    MapLoader
    This class loads the map into data structures.
    StartEditor
    The main class to initialize everything.
    Territory
    The class to load territory in data structures.
    TestMapEditor
    This class tests the functionality of map editor.
    Verification
    This class verifies map data in data structures.
